    "html": "<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\"><h3 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"74\"><strong data-start=\"4\" data-end=\"72\">Fourth Normal Form (4NF) â€“ Eliminating Multi-Valued Dependencies</strong></h3><h4 data-start=\"76\" data-end=\"98\"><strong data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"96\">Definition:</strong></h4><p data-start=\"99\" data-end=\"126\">A table is in <strong data-start=\"113\" data-end=\"120\">4NF</strong> if:</p><ol data-start=\"127\" data-end=\"257\"><li data-start=\"127\" data-end=\"204\"><strong data-start=\"130\" data-end=\"155\">It is already in BCNF</strong> (i.e., no partial or transitive dependencies).</li><li data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"257\"><strong data-start=\"208\" data-end=\"254\">It has no multi-valued dependencies (MVDs)</strong>.</li></ol><p data-start=\"259\" data-end=\"309\">A <strong data-start=\"261\" data-end=\"294\">multi-valued dependency (MVD)</strong> occurs when:</p><ul data-start=\"310\" data-end=\"421\"><li data-start=\"310\" data-end=\"421\">One <strong data-start=\"316\" data-end=\"354\">attribute can have multiple values</strong> that are <strong data-start=\"364\" data-end=\"400\">independent of another attribute</strong> in the same table.</li></ul><p data-start=\"423\" data-end=\"551\">ğŸ’¡ <strong data-start=\"426\" data-end=\"447\">In simpler terms:</strong> If one column can have multiple values <strong data-start=\"487\" data-end=\"507\">independently of</strong> another column, you should split the table.</p><hr data-start=\"553\" data-end=\"556\"><h2 data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"611\"><strong data-start=\"561\" data-end=\"611\">Different Ways a Table Can Violate 4NF &amp; Fixes</strong></h2><h3 data-start=\"613\" data-end=\"684\"><strong data-start=\"617\" data-end=\"684\">Set 1: Student and Courses vs. Sports (Multi-Valued Dependency)</strong></h3><h4 data-start=\"685\" data-end=\"710\">âŒ <strong data-start=\"692\" data-end=\"710\">Violating 4NF:</strong></h4><table data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"917\"><thead data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"744\"><tr data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"744\"><th data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"724\">Student_ID</th><th data-start=\"724\" data-end=\"734\">Course</th><th data-start=\"734\" data-end=\"744\">Sport</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"917\"><tr data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"809\"><td>1</td><td>Math</td><td>Football</td></tr><tr data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"845\"><td>1</td><td>Math</td><td>Basketball</td></tr><tr data-start=\"846\" data-end=\"880\"><td>1</td><td>Science</td><td>Football</td></tr><tr data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"917\"><td>1</td><td>Science</td><td>Basketball</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"919\" data-end=\"936\">ğŸ”´ <strong data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"934\">Problem:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"1129\"><li data-start=\"937\" data-end=\"981\">A student can take <strong data-start=\"958\" data-end=\"978\">multiple courses</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"982\" data-end=\"1025\">A student can play <strong data-start=\"1003\" data-end=\"1022\">multiple sports</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"1026\" data-end=\"1129\"><strong data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1090\">The choice of course is independent of the choice of sport</strong> â†’ <strong data-start=\"1093\" data-end=\"1126\">Multi-Valued Dependency (MVD)</strong>.</li></ul><h4 data-start=\"1131\" data-end=\"1171\">âœ… <strong data-start=\"1138\" data-end=\"1169\">Fix (Split into Two Tables)</strong></h4><p data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1200\">âœ” <strong data-start=\"1174\" data-end=\"1198\">Student-Course Table</strong></p><table data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1295\"><thead data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1225\"><tr data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1225\"><th data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1214\">Student_ID</th><th data-start=\"1214\" data-end=\"1225\">Course</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1295\"><tr data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1271\"><td>1</td><td>Math</td></tr><tr data-start=\"1272\" data-end=\"1295\"><td>1</td><td>Science</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1324\">âœ” <strong data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1322\">Student-Sport Table</strong></p><table data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1422\"><thead data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1348\"><tr data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1348\"><th data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1338\">Student_ID</th><th data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1348\">Sport</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"1371\" data-end=\"1422\"><tr data-start=\"1371\" data-end=\"1395\"><td>1</td><td>Football</td></tr><tr data-start=\"1396\" data-end=\"1422\"><td>1</td><td>Basketball</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"1424\" data-end=\"1457\">âœ… Now, the tables are in <strong data-start=\"1449\" data-end=\"1456\">4NF</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"1459\" data-end=\"1462\"><h3 data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1530\"><strong data-start=\"1468\" data-end=\"1528\">Set 2: Employee and Skills vs. Languages (MVD Violation)</strong></h3><h4 data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1556\">âŒ <strong data-start=\"1538\" data-end=\"1556\">Violating 4NF:</strong></h4><table data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1797\"><thead data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1598\"><tr data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1598\"><th data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1571\">Employee_ID</th><th data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1584\">Skill</th><th data-start=\"1584\" data-end=\"1598\">Language</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"1638\" data-end=\"1797\"><tr data-start=\"1638\" data-end=\"1677\"><td>101</td><td>Java</td><td>English</td></tr><tr data-start=\"1678\" data-end=\"1717\"><td>101</td><td>Java</td><td>French</td></tr><tr data-start=\"1718\" data-end=\"1757\"><td>101</td><td>Python</td><td>English</td></tr><tr data-start=\"1758\" data-end=\"1797\"><td>101</td><td>Python</td><td>French</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"1816\">ğŸ”´ <strong data-start=\"1802\" data-end=\"1814\">Problem:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"2021\"><li data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1862\">An employee can have <strong data-start=\"1840\" data-end=\"1859\">multiple skills</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"1863\" data-end=\"1912\">An employee can speak <strong data-start=\"1887\" data-end=\"1909\">multiple languages</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"1913\" data-end=\"2021\"><strong data-start=\"1915\" data-end=\"1982\">The knowledge of a skill is independent of language proficiency</strong> â†’ <strong data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2018\">Multi-Valued Dependency (MVD)</strong>.</li></ul><h4 data-start=\"2023\" data-end=\"2063\">âœ… <strong data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2061\">Fix (Split into Two Tables)</strong></h4><p data-start=\"2064\" data-end=\"2092\">âœ” <strong data-start=\"2066\" data-end=\"2090\">Employee-Skill Table</strong></p><table data-start=\"2093\" data-end=\"2187\"><thead data-start=\"2093\" data-end=\"2117\"><tr data-start=\"2093\" data-end=\"2117\"><th data-start=\"2093\" data-end=\"2107\">Employee_ID</th><th data-start=\"2107\" data-end=\"2117\">Skill</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2187\"><tr data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2163\"><td>101</td><td>Java</td></tr><tr data-start=\"2164\" data-end=\"2187\"><td>101</td><td>Python</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"2189\" data-end=\"2220\">âœ” <strong data-start=\"2191\" data-end=\"2218\">Employee-Language Table</strong></p><table data-start=\"2221\" data-end=\"2325\"><thead data-start=\"2221\" data-end=\"2247\"><tr data-start=\"2221\" data-end=\"2247\"><th data-start=\"2221\" data-end=\"2235\">Employee_ID</th><th data-start=\"2235\" data-end=\"2247\">Language</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"2274\" data-end=\"2325\"><tr data-start=\"2274\" data-end=\"2299\"><td>101</td><td>English</td></tr><tr data-start=\"2300\" data-end=\"2325\"><td>101</td><td>French</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"2327\" data-end=\"2360\">âœ… Now, the tables are in <strong data-start=\"2352\" data-end=\"2359\">4NF</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"2362\" data-end=\"2365\"><h3 data-start=\"2367\" data-end=\"2427\"><strong data-start=\"2371\" data-end=\"2425\">Set 3: Author and Books vs. Awards (MVD Violation)</strong></h3><h4 data-start=\"2428\" data-end=\"2453\">âŒ <strong data-start=\"2435\" data-end=\"2453\">Violating 4NF:</strong></h4><table data-start=\"2454\" data-end=\"2664\"><thead data-start=\"2454\" data-end=\"2491\"><tr data-start=\"2454\" data-end=\"2491\"><th data-start=\"2454\" data-end=\"2464\">Author</th><th data-start=\"2464\" data-end=\"2478\">Book</th><th data-start=\"2478\" data-end=\"2491\">Award</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"2525\" data-end=\"2664\"><tr data-start=\"2525\" data-end=\"2559\"><td>Alice</td><td>Book A</td><td>Nobel</td></tr><tr data-start=\"2560\" data-end=\"2594\"><td>Alice</td><td>Book A</td><td>Pulitzer</td></tr><tr data-start=\"2595\" data-end=\"2629\"><td>Alice</td><td>Book B</td><td>Nobel</td></tr><tr data-start=\"2630\" data-end=\"2664\"><td>Alice</td><td>Book B</td><td>Pulitzer</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"2666\" data-end=\"2683\">ğŸ”´ <strong data-start=\"2669\" data-end=\"2681\">Problem:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"2684\" data-end=\"2874\"><li data-start=\"2684\" data-end=\"2727\">An <strong data-start=\"2689\" data-end=\"2724\">author can write multiple books</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"2728\" data-end=\"2774\">An <strong data-start=\"2733\" data-end=\"2771\">author can receive multiple awards</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"2775\" data-end=\"2874\"><strong data-start=\"2777\" data-end=\"2835\">The book written is independent of the awards received</strong> â†’ <strong data-start=\"2838\" data-end=\"2871\">Multi-Valued Dependency (MVD)</strong>.</li></ul><h4 data-start=\"2876\" data-end=\"2916\">âœ… <strong data-start=\"2883\" data-end=\"2914\">Fix (Split into Two Tables)</strong></h4><p data-start=\"2917\" data-end=\"2942\">âœ” <strong data-start=\"2919\" data-end=\"2940\">Author-Book Table</strong></p><table data-start=\"2943\" data-end=\"3020\"><thead data-start=\"2943\" data-end=\"2962\"><tr data-start=\"2943\" data-end=\"2962\"><th data-start=\"2943\" data-end=\"2953\">Author</th><th data-start=\"2953\" data-end=\"2962\">Book</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"2981\" data-end=\"3020\"><tr data-start=\"2981\" data-end=\"3000\"><td>Alice</td><td>Book A</td></tr><tr data-start=\"3001\" data-end=\"3020\"><td>Alice</td><td>Book B</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"3022\" data-end=\"3048\">âœ” <strong data-start=\"3024\" data-end=\"3046\">Author-Award Table</strong></p><table data-start=\"3049\" data-end=\"3137\"><thead data-start=\"3049\" data-end=\"3072\"><tr data-start=\"3049\" data-end=\"3072\"><th data-start=\"3049\" data-end=\"3059\">Author</th><th data-start=\"3059\" data-end=\"3072\">Award</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"3094\" data-end=\"3137\"><tr data-start=\"3094\" data-end=\"3115\"><td>Alice</td><td>Nobel</td></tr><tr data-start=\"3116\" data-end=\"3137\"><td>Alice</td><td>Pulitzer</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"3139\" data-end=\"3172\">âœ… Now, the tables are in <strong data-start=\"3164\" data-end=\"3171\">4NF</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"3174\" data-end=\"3177\"><h2 data-start=\"3179\" data-end=\"3199\"><strong data-start=\"3182\" data-end=\"3199\">Summary Table</strong></h2><table data-start=\"3200\" data-end=\"3842\"><thead data-start=\"3200\" data-end=\"3251\"><tr data-start=\"3200\" data-end=\"3251\"><th data-start=\"3200\" data-end=\"3221\"><strong data-start=\"3202\" data-end=\"3220\">Violation Type</strong></th><th data-start=\"3221\" data-end=\"3235\"><strong data-start=\"3223\" data-end=\"3234\">Example</strong></th><th data-start=\"3235\" data-end=\"3251\"><strong data-start=\"3237\" data-end=\"3249\">Solution</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody data-start=\"3302\" data-end=\"3842\"><tr data-start=\"3302\" data-end=\"3472\"><td><strong data-start=\"3304\" data-end=\"3377\">A student enrolls in courses and plays sports, but they are unrelated</strong></td><td><code data-start=\"3380\" data-end=\"3409\">{Student_ID, Course, Sport}</code></td><td>Split into <strong data-start=\"3423\" data-end=\"3441\">Student-Course</strong> and <strong data-start=\"3446\" data-end=\"3463\">Student-Sport</strong> tables</td></tr><tr data-start=\"3473\" data-end=\"3666\"><td><strong data-start=\"3475\" data-end=\"3564\">An employee has multiple skills and speaks multiple languages, but they are unrelated</strong></td><td><code data-start=\"3567\" data-end=\"3599\">{Employee_ID, Skill, Language}</code></td><td>Split into <strong data-start=\"3613\" data-end=\"3631\">Employee-Skill</strong> and <strong data-start=\"3636\" data-end=\"3657\">Employee-Language</strong> tables</td></tr><tr data-start=\"3667\" data-end=\"3842\"><td><strong data-start=\"3669\" data-end=\"3757\">An author writes multiple books and receives multiple awards, but they are unrelated</strong></td><td><code data-start=\"3760\" data-end=\"3783\">{Author, Book, Award}</code></td><td>Split into <strong data-start=\"3797\" data-end=\"3812\">Author-Book</strong> and <strong data-start=\"3817\" data-end=\"3833\">Author-Award</strong> tables</td></tr></tbody></table><p data-start=\"3844\" data-end=\"3887\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Would you like more real-world examples? ğŸ˜Š</p></div>"
